00:11:52,828 --> 00:11:54,425
alts oyf ivrit

203
00:11:54,904 --> 00:11:56,715
hobn mir geredt dortn.

204
00:11:56,715 --> 00:12:02,070
le- do zitst di GANENET. a mol hot men dos gerufn DODA SARA.

205
00:12:02,498 --> 00:12:06,620
un di tsveyte froy vos shteyt iz DODA RIVKA.

206
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:10,831
lebn DODA SARA fun rekhts zits ikh.

207
00:12:10,831 --> 00:12:14,676
do bin ikh mistome a yor zeks, vi ikh farshtey.

208
00:12:15,475 --> 00:12:19,606
lebn, di tsveyte zayt, lebn di DODA SARA zitst a meydele,

209
00:12:19,606 --> 00:12:21,239
Henele ⟨Slaveyt⟩.

210
00:12:21,263 --> 00:12:25,877
zey zaynen avek f- fun Kretinge avekgeforn nokh far der milkhome

211
00:12:25,877 --> 00:12:29,002
in toyznt nayn hundert zeks un draysikstn yor.

212
00:12:29,002 --> 00:12:31,297
lebt yetst in PETAKH TIKVA.

213
00:12:32,012 --> 00:12:35,347
lebn DODA RIVKA, fun di linke zayt,

214
00:12:35,387 --> 00:12:36,208
der o-

215
00:12:36,265 --> 00:12:38,537
Fayve Olshvang.

216
00:12:38,931 --> 00:12:41,034
er iz oykh in Yisroel yetst.

217
00:12:42,711 --> 00:12:46,507
nu, un di iberike ale kinderlekh nokh do,

218
00:12:46,507 --> 00:12:49,234
ale zaynen umgekumen in tsayt fun di SHOAH

219
00:12:49,234 --> 00:12:51,314
bay undz in shtetl Kretinge.

220
00:12:55,806 --> 00:12:58,922
do iz mayn zeyde AHARON

221
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:02,887
un mayn babe Basye Mendelovitsh.

222
00:13:04,530 --> 00:13:07,494
oyfn tsveytn bild, oyf di, oyfn BET

223
00:13:07,568 --> 00:13:09,097
HAKVAROT

224
00:13:09,323 --> 00:13:15,085
bay di matseyve fun mayn zeydn vos iz geshtorbn in toyznt nayn hundert akht un draysikstn yor.

225
00:13:15,085 --> 00:13:18,653
fun di rekhte zayt di ershte shtey i- ikh,

226
00:13:18,653 --> 00:13:23,672
Sheyte, mayn muter DORA un mayn foter Beynish.

227
00:13:23,672 --> 00:13:30,731
fun di tsveyte zayt fun keyver shteyt mayn kuzine Rokhele vos lebt yetst in RAMAT GAN,

228
00:13:30,788 --> 00:13:33,356
ir mame, Feyge,

229
00:13:33,356 --> 00:13:36,504
vos iz derharget gevorn i- bay undz in Kretinge

230
00:13:36,504 --> 00:13:38,368
fun di litvishe rotskhim,

231
00:13:38,368 --> 00:13:40,254
un mayn tante RIVKA,

232
00:13:40,254 --> 00:13:43,254
vos iz geshtorbn in Rusland in Sibir.

233
00:13:43,647 --> 00:13:45,480
vos iz geshen mit der babe?

234
00:13:45,381 --> 00:13:50,597
di babe iz oykh umgekumen bay undz in shtetl in nayntsn, in di ershte teg fun di milkhome,

235
00:13:50,597 --> 00:13:53,995
tsuzamen mit mayn mame un mit mayn bruder.

236
00:13:54,430 --> 00:13:55,757
in velkhn yor?

237
00:13:55,420 --> 00:13:57,309
nayntsn eyn un fertsik.

238
00:14:02,648 --> 00:14:09,228
dos iz a bildele fun gimnazye fun n- toyznt nayn hundert nayn un draysikstn yor,

239
00:14:09,228 --> 00:14:11,841
vos iz geven PRANCIŠKONŲ

240
00:14:11,841 --> 00:14:15,226
gimnazye nor hey- nor fun meydlekh.

241
00:14:15,226 --> 00:14:18,260
do in mitn, di tsveyte rey,

242
00:14:18,260 --> 00:14:20,397
in mitn zits ikh.

243
00:14:20,397 --> 00:14:22,715
un fun di linke zayt

244
00:14:22,715 --> 00:14:27,078
sh- di, shteyt a meydl, mayne a zeyer gute khaverte,

245
00:14:27,078 --> 00:14:28,931
me ruft ir ⟨Pyatre⟩.

246
00:14:28,931 --> 00:14:32,169
zi lebt yetst in Lite in Palange.

247
00:14:32,169 --> 00:14:35,169
di gantse fuftsik yor nokh di milkhome

248
00:14:35,169 --> 00:14:37,442
hobn mir zikh zeyer mit ir gekhavert.

249
00:14:38,946 --> 00:14:42,124
un ale andere meydlekh vos alts, alts ⟨kristishe⟩ meyd-

250
00:14:40,386 --> 00:14:43,647
ale ander- alts krist- litvishe meydlekh,

251
00:14:43,647 --> 00:14:46,033
eyne do shteyt a, vos iz shoyn geshtorbn,

252
00:14:46,033 --> 00:14:48,283
di iberike veys ikh nit vu zey zaynen.

253
00:14:51,788 --> 00:14:57,907
dos bin ikh in toyznt nayn hundert nayn un draysikstn yor als studentin

254
00:14:58,487 --> 00:14:59,763
fun gimnazye,

255
00:14:59,989 --> 00:15:01,552
in K- Kretinge.

256
00:15:05,085 --> 00:15:06,243
do

257
00:15:06,283 --> 00:15:07,947
der, bin ikh

258
00:15:08,308 --> 00:15:09,939
mit mayn man,

259
00:15:09,962 --> 00:15:14,633
in nayntsn zek- in toyznt nayn hundert zeks un fertsikstn yor

260
00:15:14,633 --> 00:15:17,860
mit di, undzer meyde- tokhterl, DORA,

261
00:15:17,860 --> 00:15:20,042
vos s'iz ir zibn monat.

262
00:15:19,952 --> 00:15:22,274
un dos iz gemakht gevorn vu?

263
00:15:21,477 --> 00:15:23,118
⟨gevo-⟩ in, in Kovne.

264
00:15:23,935 --> 00:15:25,318
glaykh nokh der milkhome.

265
00:15:25,136 --> 00:15:25,481
ye.

266
00:15:29,453 --> 00:15:35,737
do bin ikh mit mayn man Elyezer in toyznt nayn hundert tsvey un zekhtsikstn yor

267
00:15:35,737 --> 00:15:38,533
in Kovne, bay undz in shtub.

268
00:15:44,539 --> 00:15:46,406
ven iz dos geven? velkhe yor?

269
00:15:46,204 --> 00:15:49,640
dos iz yetst geven, in zeks, in zeks un nayntsikstn yor.

270
00:15:47,138 --> 00:15:49,874
letstns? OKAY.

271
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:50,770
in oktober.

272
00:15:50,775 --> 00:15:51,511
⟨GOOD.⟩

273
00:15:52,470 --> 00:15:57,312
dos iz der bild fun bar-mitsve fun undzer eynikl MIKHAIL,

274
00:15:57,312 --> 00:16:01,324
in toyznt nayn hundert zeks un nayntsikstn yor, in oktober monat,

275
00:16:01,324 --> 00:16:04,233
in ULAM ERMITAZH in ASHDOD.

276
00:16:04,890 --> 00:16:06,030
do zi-

277
00:16:05,234 --> 00:16:06,689
ver iz, ver iz oyfn bild?

278
00:16:07,135 --> 00:16:09,812
do z- fun rekhts zits ikh,

279
00:16:09,970 --> 00:16:12,951
lebn mir mayn man, ELIEZER,

280
00:16:13,648 --> 00:16:16,055
undzer tokhter SONYA,

281
00:16:16,365 --> 00:16:18,586
ir man ELI,

282
00:16:18,930 --> 00:16:22,669
zeyer tokhterl, undzer eynikl KARMELA,

283
00:16:22,669 --> 00:16:27,214
un der bar-mitsve-bokher MIKHAIL, undzer eynikl.

284
00:16:28,768 --> 00:16:30,314
⟨hobn⟩ di hazkore.

285
00:16:32,194 --> 00:16:37,925
dos iz oykhet oyf di, di bal-mitsve fun undzer eynikl MIKHAIL in ULAM

286
00:16:38,910 --> 00:16:39,950
ARMITAZH.

287
00:16:39,772 --> 00:16:41,329
ERMITAZH

288
00:16:41,329 --> 00:16:46,903
in toyznt nayn hundert zeks un nayntsikstn yor in oktober. do zitst fun rekhts

289
00:16:47,112 --> 00:16:50,059
undzer eydem MOSHE.

290
00:16:50,402 --> 00:16:56,741
lebn im di, undzer tokhterl DORA, di froy fun MOSHE.

291
00:16:57,000 --> 00:17:00,439
di, zeyer tokhter ILANA.

292
00:17:00,439 --> 00:17:04,993
oyfn hant halt zi ir tekhterl DORIN.

293
00:17:05,488 --> 00:17:07,912
lebn ir zitst ir man

294
00:17:08,357 --> 00:17:09,481
BARUKH.

295
00:17:10,213 --> 00:17:14,772
es shteyen di tsveyte tokhter, SONYA,

296
00:17:14,772 --> 00:17:18,954
der bar-mitsve-bokher M- MIKHAIL,

297
00:17:18,954 --> 00:17:21,511
undzer eynikl,

298
00:17:21,511 --> 00:17:25,579
zeyer tokhter KARMELA, undzer eynikl,

299
00:17:25,579 --> 00:17:28,636
un zey, der man, der foter fun di

300
00:17:28,636 --> 00:17:31,375
fun di mishpokhe, ELI.

301
00:17:31,375 --> 00:17:33,242
in, oykh in ASHDOD.

302
00:17:35,830 --> 00:17:41,528
do zaynen beyde groyse eyniklekh fun undzer eltere tokhter DORA,

303
00:17:41,652 --> 00:17:43,108
ILANA,

304
00:17:43,108 --> 00:17:44,311
vos iz

305
00:17:44,487 --> 00:17:48,885
yetst in shtub. zi hodevet a yingele fun zibn monat.

306
00:17:49,195 --> 00:17:51,517
der eynikl ALON.

307
00:17:51,608 --> 00:17:53,660
er iz yetst in TSAVA.

308
00:17:58,543 --> 00:18:02,469
do zitsn mir. do iz mayn man, ELIEZER,

309
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:06,311
vos mir zaynen shoyn bakant f- fuftsik yor,

310
00:18:06,311 --> 00:18:10,369
fun nayntsn f- finf un fertsik, AVGUST monat,

311
00:18:10,369 --> 00:18:15,665
lebn mir shoyn tsuzamen, shoyn opgefayert di v- goldene khasene.

312
00:18:18,422 --> 00:18:20,019
her ELIEZER,

313
00:18:20,059 --> 00:18:22,854
ir zitst yetst lebn ayer froy

314
00:18:22,978 --> 00:18:26,215
vos hot, mir hobn yetst geendikt mit ir a intervyu.

315
00:18:26,215 --> 00:18:30,617
ir zent dokh oykhet a gelitener, ir hot oykh durkhgegangen di SHOAH,

316
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:35,055
volt ikh aykh gevolt betn, ir zolt zogn etlekhe verter oyb s'iz meglekh.

317
00:22:55,712 --> 00:22:57,528
ikh volt aykh gevolt nokh a mol

318
00:22:58,328 --> 00:22:59,843
beyde danken

319
00:22:59,843 --> 00:23:03,418
far der onshtrengung ⟨ir makht⟩ undz tsu dertseyln ayere zikhroynes.

320
00:23:04,335 --> 00:23:06,630
un mit dem farendikn mir undzer intervyu.

321
00:23:06,816 --> 00:23:08,480
UNK a groysn dank.

322
00:26:07,280 --> 00:26:09,045
TODA RABA. KOL HAKAVOD.

